    • Method Detail

      • open

        InputStream open()
        Open the resource or file and return the input stream. If the path is prefixed with classpath: then it is treated as a classpath resource. Otherwise, it is assumed to be a file system path.
        Returns:
        The input stream or null if the file or resource cannot be found.
